folder: Park Avenue & Vanderbilt Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
223-229 Park Avenue, north side, between Vanderbilt and Clinton Avenues, showing old frame homes, recently stuccoed. View 1 shows only Nos. 22-229, looking toward Clinton Avenue, viewing westward.

P. L. Sperr

View 1: July 22, 1934
View 3: April 12, 1941
